---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Your Health Journey — 5 Levels" description="A gradual approach to living healthier. Start where you are, move at your own pace.">
  <div class="levels-intro">
    <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Home</a>
    <h1>Your Health Journey</h1>
    <p>You don't have to change everything overnight. This is a gradual path — start with the free, easy wins and go deeper when you're ready. Each level builds on the last.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="levels-grid">
    <section class="level-card level-1">
      <div class="level-badge">Level 1</div>
      <h2>Quick Wins</h2>
      <p class="level-subtitle">Free or nearly free. Start today.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Stop <a href="/microplastics/reducing-exposure">microwaving food in plastic</a> — use a plate or glass container</li>
        <li>Stop drinking from plastic bottles left in hot cars</li>
        <li>Open windows 15 minutes a day for <a href="/indoor-air-quality/indoor-pollutants">ventilation</a></li>
        <li>Read ingredient labels — avoid <a href="/food-additives/food-dyes">Red 40, Yellow 5</a>, high fructose corn syrup</li>
        <li>Wash produce before eating</li>
        <li>Ditch <a href="/household-chemicals/candles-and-air-fresheners">plug-in air fresheners</a> — just open a window</li>
        <li>Practice <a href="/mouth-breathing/why-nose-breathing-matters">nose breathing</a> during the day</li>
        <li>Take a <a href="/walking/most-underrated-exercise">10-minute walk</a> after meals</li>
        <li>Get <a href="/sunlight/more-than-vitamin-d">morning sunlight</a> within 30 minutes of waking</li>
        <li>Start <a href="/intermittent-fasting/what-is-fasting">closing your eating window</a> — try 12 hours to start</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="level-card level-2">
      <div class="level-badge">Level 2</div>
      <h2>Easy Swaps</h2>
      <p class="level-subtitle">Small cost. Do over a few weeks.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Switch cooking oil to <a href="/olive-oil">olive oil</a>, avocado oil, butter, or ghee — <a href="/seed-oils/what-are-seed-oils">ditch seed oils</a></li>
        <li>Get a basic <a href="/water-filtration/choosing-a-filter">water filter</a> pitcher</li>
        <li>Switch to <a href="/personal-care-products/deodorant">aluminum-free deodorant</a></li>
        <li>Switch to <a href="/sunscreen/choosing-safe-sunscreen">mineral sunscreen</a> (zinc oxide)</li>
        <li>Replace plastic food storage with glass as old ones wear out</li>
        <li>Buy one <a href="/non-stick-cookware/safer-cookware">cast iron or stainless steel</a> pan</li>
        <li>Buy the Dirty Dozen produce organic</li>
        <li>Switch to <a href="/tea/loose-leaf-vs-bags">loose leaf tea</a></li>
        <li>Start taking <a href="/vitamin-d/supplementation">vitamin D3</a> + <a href="/vitamin-k2/calcium-routing">K2</a></li>
        <li>Add <a href="/magnesium/types-of-magnesium">magnesium glycinate</a> before bed</li>
        <li>Replace <a href="/artificial-sweeteners/the-sweetener-problem">artificial sweeteners</a> with stevia or monk fruit</li>
        <li>Use <a href="/dental-health/nano-hydroxyapatite">nano-hydroxyapatite toothpaste</a> instead of fluoride</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="level-card level-3">
      <div class="level-badge">Level 3</div>
      <h2>Leveling Up</h2>
      <p class="level-subtitle">Moderate investment. Over a few months.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Switch to natural <a href="/household-chemicals/cleaning-products">cleaning products</a> (or DIY with vinegar and castile soap)</li>
        <li>Get a quality under-sink or countertop <a href="/water-filtration/choosing-a-filter">water filter</a></li>
        <li>Switch <a href="/personal-care-products/shampoo-and-body-care">personal care products</a> — clean shampoo, body wash, toothpaste</li>
        <li>Buy pasture-raised <a href="/eggs/the-perfect-food">eggs</a>, <a href="/grass-fed-meat/why-it-matters">grass-fed meat</a></li>
        <li><a href="/farm-raised-fish/choosing-safe-seafood">Wild-caught fish</a> only</li>
        <li>Replace all <a href="/non-stick-cookware/safer-cookware">non-stick cookware</a></li>
        <li>Get an <a href="/indoor-air-quality/air-purifiers-and-filters">air purifier</a> for your bedroom</li>
        <li>Switch to soy or beeswax <a href="/household-chemicals/candles-and-air-fresheners">candles</a></li>
        <li>Fragrance-free <a href="/household-chemicals/laundry-products">laundry detergent</a>, wool dryer balls</li>
        <li>Add <a href="/omega-3-fatty-acids/sources-and-dosing">omega-3</a> and <a href="/probiotics/food-vs-supplements">probiotics</a></li>
        <li>Start eating <a href="/fermented-foods/living-foods">fermented foods</a> daily</li>
        <li>Begin a <a href="/resistance-training/getting-started">resistance training</a> routine</li>
        <li>Start a <a href="/meditation-breathwork/breathing-techniques">breathwork</a> practice</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="level-card level-4">
      <div class="level-badge">Level 4</div>
      <h2>Going Deep</h2>
      <p class="level-subtitle">Significant lifestyle shifts.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Go mostly organic across the board</li>
        <li>Whole-house or under-sink reverse osmosis water filter</li>
        <li>Shower filter for chlorine</li>
        <li>Organic, non-toxic <a href="/mattresses-furniture/non-toxic-alternatives">mattress and bedding</a></li>
        <li>Low-VOC everything — paint, furniture, flooring</li>
        <li>All clean <a href="/personal-care-products/cosmetics-and-makeup">beauty and personal care</a> products</li>
        <li>HEPA + activated carbon <a href="/indoor-air-quality/air-purifiers-and-filters">air filtration</a></li>
        <li>Source local — farmers markets, CSA boxes</li>
        <li>Add <a href="/organ-meats/natures-multivitamin">organ meats</a> or desiccated liver capsules</li>
        <li>Regular <a href="/sauna/infrared-vs-traditional">sauna</a> and <a href="/cold-exposure/protocols-and-safety">cold exposure</a></li>
        <li>Consider a <a href="/parasite-cleansing/protocols">parasite cleanse</a></li>
        <li>Support <a href="/liver-cleansing/supporting-detox-pathways">liver detox pathways</a></li>
        <li>Get <a href="/thyroid-health/the-master-gland">thyroid panels</a> and <a href="/heavy-metal-detox/sources-and-testing">heavy metal testing</a></li>
        <li>Optimize <a href="/sleep/sleep-hygiene">sleep environment</a> — temperature, darkness, air quality</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="level-card level-5">
      <div class="level-badge">Level 5</div>
      <h2>Full Optimization</h2>
      <p class="level-subtitle">The complete picture.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Fully organic, whole-food diet — nothing processed</li>
        <li>Zero plastic in the kitchen</li>
        <li>Full home air and water filtration</li>
        <li>All non-toxic home — furniture, paint, flooring, mattress</li>
        <li><a href="/mouth-breathing/how-to-switch">Nose breathing</a> practice, <a href="/cold-exposure/brown-fat-and-metabolism">cold exposure</a>, <a href="/grounding/earthing-science">grounding</a></li>
        <li><a href="/vagus-nerve/stimulation-techniques">Vagus nerve</a> stimulation daily</li>
        <li><a href="/forest-bathing/shinrin-yoku">Forest bathing</a> weekly</li>
        <li><a href="/zone-2-cardio/mitochondrial-fitness">Zone 2 cardio</a> 3-4 hours/week</li>
        <li>Know your farmer for meat, eggs, and dairy</li>
        <li>Grow a portion of your own food</li>
        <li>Regular <a href="/journaling/write-to-heal">journaling</a> and <a href="/meditation-breathwork/stress-and-brain">meditation</a></li>
        <li><a href="/digital-detox/reclaiming-attention">Digital sabbath</a> weekly</li>
        <li>Annual functional medicine checkup</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="levels-cta">
    <p>Every change matters. You don't need to reach Level 5 — even a few Level 1 changes can transform how you feel.</p>
    <div class="cta-links">
      <a href="/" class="cta-button">Explore Topics</a>
      <a href="/lookup" class="cta-button-outline">What should I take for...?</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .levels-intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .levels-intro h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .levels-intro p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 36rem;
  }

  .levels-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .level-card {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .level-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .level-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs) 0;
  }

  .level-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md) 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .level-card ul {
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .level-card li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .level-1 { border-left-color: #4ade80; }
  .level-2 { border-left-color: #60a5fa; }
  .level-3 { border-left-color: #f59e0b; }
  .level-4 { border-left-color: #f97316; }
  .level-5 { border-left-color: #a855f7; }

  .level-1 .level-badge { color: #4ade80; }
  .level-2 .level-badge { color: #60a5fa; }
  .level-3 .level-badge { color: #f59e0b; }
  .level-4 .level-badge { color: #f97316; }
  .level-5 .level-badge { color: #a855f7; }

  .levels-cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .levels-cta p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .cta-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.15s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-button-outline {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }

  .cta-button-outline:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
</style>
